     <div class="content-column maincontent" id="primary-column">
      <div class="region region-home-center">
       <div class="block block-block first last odd module clearfix" id="block-block-11">
        <h2 class="block__title block-title">
         Welcome
        </h2>
        <div class="block-content">
         <p>
          Under the leadership of Kim Taylor, Vice President and General Counsel, the Office of Legal Counsel advises University officials on legal and regulatory questions associated with the University’s activities (including transactional matters, policy formulation and compliance, employment and student issues, and pre-litigation dispute resolution), and represents the interests of the University in administrative and judicial proceedings.
         </p>
         <p>
          Learn more about the
          <a href="http://legalcounsel-sites.uchicago.edu/page/about-office">
           functions of our office
          </a>
          and
          <a href="http://legalcounsel-sites.uchicago.edu/directories/full/olc-attorneys">
           our attorneys
          </a>
          .
         </p>
         <p>
          <a href="http://legalcounsel-sites.uchicago.edu/directories/table/contact-us">
           Contact the Office of Legal Counsel
          </a>
          for more information.
         </p>
        </div>
       </div>
